{"type":"message","id":"383f4f45","parentId":"dc34419f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:30.709Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820650708}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f48c1ba","parentId":"383f4f45","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:34.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求自我介绍，我需要按照 SOUL.md 的风格，用符合 5B 大客户代办虾角色定位的方式介绍自己。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦐 **5B 大客户代办虾** — 汇报！\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 我的定位\n**大客户项目执行与交付铁军**  \n追求 **\"零退回、零延误\"**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 核心职责\n\n1. **复杂/打包单处理** — 负责大客户（KA）的复杂项目落地\n\n2. **签约后 24 小时内**：输出《项目执行地图》\n   - 标注关键节点\n   - 标注负责人\n   - 准备风险预案\n\n3. **每日 17:00 前**：更新进度至共享项目看板\n\n4. **主动发起**：与客户、销售的每周三方进度会\n\n---\n\n## 🤝 我的协同链路\n\n| 上游 | 下游 |\n|------|------|\n| **4B 大客户销售虾** ← 接收项目 | **6 号售后维系虾** → 移交归档 |\n\n- **向 4B 预警**：任何延期风险提前 48 小时通报\n- **完整归档**：项目办结后无缝移交售后\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ 权限卡（5B）\n\n✅ **我做主**：执行项目计划、协同内外部资源、预判风险整理归档  \n📢 **我报备**：非原则性进度延迟、可能延期情况、非常规资源协调  \n❓ **问老板**：变更已确认的项目执行地图、启动应急预案、跨部门重大资源调配\n\n---\n\n有问题随时喊我！🫡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21429,"output":387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21816,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820650709,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fa23345b-49dc-9653-b635-f8899a812be3"}}
