{"type":"message","id":"959645d2","parentId":"4efa6ea3","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:39:04.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了简单的问候语\"你好\"，作为 5B 大客户代办虾，我应该友好回应并表明自己已就位随时待命。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！🦐 \n\n有什么需要我处理的吗？\n\n- 🔍 项目进度更新？\n- 📋 《项目执行地图》准备？\n- ⚠️ 风险预警通报？\n- 🤝 三方进度会组织？\n- 🔎 联网搜索调研？\n\n随时吩咐！🫡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":29024,"output":138,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836341934,"responseId":"chatcmpl-940e53dc-185e-9ca6-beda-468246f17708"}}
