{"type":"message","id":"47974331","parentId":"fff8ba6b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:29.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"记忆文件已写入完成，需要向用户确认更新结果并提供技能核心要点总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **学习完成！已保存到记忆**\n\n我已在 `memory/2026-04-22-agent-browser-skills.md` 中详细记录了 `agent-browser` 技能的使用方法：\n\n---\n\n## 📌 核心要点速记\n\n| 要点 | 说明 |\n|:---|:---|\n| **命令入口** | `agent-browser <command>` |\n| **标准快照** | `agent-browser snapshot -i --json` |\n| **元素引用** | `@e1`, `@e2`, ... 从 JSON 解析 |\n| **Session 隔离** | `--session admin` / `--session user` |\n| **状态持久化** | `state save/load auth.json` 跳过登录 |\n| **等待策略** | `wait --load networkidle` |\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 典型工作流\n\n```bash\n# 打开页面 → 快照 → 解析 refs → 交互 → 再快照\nagent-browser open https://example.com\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json   # 获取 @e1, @e2...\nagent-browser fill @e1 \"text\"      # 使用 ref 交互\nagent-browser press Enter\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json   # 重新获取新 refs\n```\n\n---\n\n这个技能的优势是**速度快、确定性高**，特别适合复杂的自动化流程和多账号并行测试场景。🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33114,"output":355,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33469,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836785212,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a85ef618-f32d-9553-b515-10a8bac47a3b"}}
