{"type":"message","id":"cce01925","parentId":"4a89b1d1","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:39:51.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件已写入记忆，需要向用户确认学习完成并简要总结这个技能的核心要点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **学习完成！已保存到记忆**\n\n我已在 `memory/2026-04-22-self-improving-proactive-agent.md` 中详细记录了 Self-Improving Proactive Agent 技能的使用方法：\n\n---\n\n## 📌 核心双架构速记\n\n| 层 | 作用 | 关键文件 |\n|:---|:---|:---|\n| **🧠 Self-Improving** | 从修正中学习、记住偏好 | `memory.md`, `corrections.md` |\n| **⚡ Proactive** | 推动工作前进、恢复上下文 | `session-state.md`, `patterns.md` |\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 六大原则牢记\n\n1. **只从显式证据学习** - 不听沉默、不猜感觉\n2. **推动下一步有用的动作** - 草稿/检查/推荐优先\n3. **信息路由到正确位置** - HOT vs session vs buffer\n4. **问之前先恢复上下文** - 5 步读取法\n5. **验证实现不只是意图** - 测结果再报告\n6. **硬边界内保持主动** - 花钱/发消息/删数据先问\n\n---\n\n## 💾 OpenClaw 文件映射\n\n```yaml\n~/self-improving/memory.md        → AGENTS.md\n~/self-improving/corrections.md   → HEARTBEAT.md  \n~/self-improving/index.md         → MEMORY.md\n~/proactivity/memory.md           → TOOLS.md\n```\n\nOpenClaw 会自动从这些标准配置路径加载！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":37754,"output":386,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776839985584,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ae99796d-a465-99da-a817-b7492bc190c3"}}
